snippet.title: Best VGM 1702 - The Legend of Heroes : Trails in the Sky - Tetracyclic Tower
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC / PSP / Vita / PS3
The Legend of Heroes : Trails in the Sky (2004)
Tetracyclic Tower
Falcom Sound Team JDK (Hayato Sonoda, Wataru Ishibashi, Takahide Murayama)
